{"tid":1041572,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Fresh Grad圍爐打氣區👩🏻‍🎓其實畢業又有咩好怕喎","createTime":"2019-03-01T02:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T15:44:06.000Z","uid":114539,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0dd254cf41f95b3343b898e6920a0f22d943c9","tid":1041572,"uid":114539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T02:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hello 各位囉囉攣嘅fresh grad <br />\n雖然未到畢業季<br />\n但總有啲迷途小羔羊返咗幾個月工就心思思想轉工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲嚟緊畢又做晒fyp等攞cert嘅<br />\nfinal year得閒睇下有咩好工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有啲好似我咁defer嘅老人家而家先出嚟搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 希望呢個post可以同各位fresh grad bb討論下近況/搵工情況/交換下消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗怕醜 嚟啦各位fresh grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算你唔係fresh grad<br />\n想轉工搵工都歡迎你地留下名字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUpdate下自己近況先：<br />\nDefer半年<br />\n啱啱先的起心肝搵工<br />\n咩到範疇嘅工都涉獵下<br />\nAssistant, receptionist, clerk...咩都搵過<br />\n第一份一in就俾offer我<br />\n但係工作時間同人工我覺得仲需要時間考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948a707496f3874c5651b051f4c7bc80b88c809f","tid":1041572,"uid":114539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh<br />\n醒喇咁多位fresh grad bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6a2021466e75c6f2ef9933eb6135c4edb66e39","tid":1041572,"uid":32324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"Final yr 成行都無ft post<br />\n依家有人搭路，睇下開個低啲既post<br />\n諗緊take唔take 